===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ɡɹɪŋɡəʊ/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|ɪŋɡəʊ|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|gringoes}}

# {{label|en|slang|often|pejorative|in Latin America}} a white person from an English-speaking country.

